               Notes
              </h3>
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              Your return value must be within 1e-9 absolute or relative of the actual value.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
